uline/webp/dance/F_Dances_001.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%;\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003cdiv align=\"middle\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/masculine/fbx/dance\"\u003eDance\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/masculine/webp/expression/F_Talking_Variations_004.webp\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/raw/master/masculine/webp/expression/F_Talking_Variations_004.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%;\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003cdiv align=\"middle\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/masculine/fbx/expression\"\u003eExpression\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\n\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/masculine/webp/idle/F_Standing_Idle_Variations_001.webp\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/raw/master/masculine/webp/idle/F_Standing_Idle_Variations_001.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%;\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003cdiv align=\"middle\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/masculine/fbx/idle\"\u003eIdle\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/markdown-accessiblity-table\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eFAQ\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-faq\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: FAQ\" href=\"#faq\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eAre these animations really free?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-are-these-animations-really-free\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Are these animations really free?\" href=\"#are-these-animations-really-free\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eYes, free as in beer! We created this animation library to help the game development community create more unique and engaging experiences. This is just the first batch of many more free releases. Please read our \u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/LICENSE.md\"\u003elicense for more details\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eCan I use these animations with characters that are not from Ready Player Me?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-can-i-use-these-animations-with-characters-that-are-not-from-ready-player-me\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Can I use these animations with characters that are not from Ready Player Me?\" href=\"#can-i-use-these-animations-with-characters-that-are-not-from-ready-player-me\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThe animations are specifically designed for Ready Player Me avatars and are not intended to be used with other characters.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eWhen will more animations be released?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-when-will-more-animations-be-released\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: When will more animations be released?\" href=\"#when-will-more-animations-be-released\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThis is just the first batch of animations we're releasing to the community. We will continue releasing animations throughout 2023 and beyond.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eWhat software do I need to use with these animations?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-what-software-do-i-need-to-use-with-these-animations\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: What software do I need to use with these animations?\" href=\"#what-software-do-i-need-to-use-with-these-animations\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eYou can use any software that supports the FBX file type, including Unity, Unreal Engine, Blender, Maya, Sketchfab, etc.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eWhere can I get help using these animations?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-where-can-i-get-help-using-these-animations\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Where can I get help using these animations?\" href=\"#where-can-i-get-help-using-these-animations\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003ePlease check out the tutorial below. If you're already a Ready Player Me partner you can email \u003ca href=\"mailto:support@readyplayer.me\"\u003esupport@readyplayer.me\u003c/a\u003e with additional questions, or sign up as a developer at \u003ca href=\"https://readyplayer.me/developers\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ereadyplayer.me/developers\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eTutorials\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-tutorials\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Tutorials\" href=\"#tutorials\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eWe provide the following general guides to loading the provided animations on Ready Player Me avatars in Unity and Unreal Engine. However, other approaches and configurations maybe required depending on your own project needs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/guides/Unity-Guide.md\"\u003eUsing animations in Unity\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"/readyplayerme/animation-library/blob/master/guides/Unreal-Guide.md\"\u003eUsing animations in Unreal\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eWe always aim to provide our partners with the highest quality assets, please let us know if you encounter any issues using these animations on your loaded Ready Player Me avatars, such as mesh deformation problems in extreme poses or any unexpected behaviour during playback.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eNotes\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-notes\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Notes\" href=\"#notes\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eIn order to properly use this repository, you need to have Git Large File Storage (LFS) installed on your system.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThe animation filename prefix denotes which actor gender was used to generate the motion:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cmarkdown-accessiblity-table\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eFilename prefix\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eM_\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eMotion captured from male actor\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eF_\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eMotion captured from female actress\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/markdown-accessiblity-table\u003e\n\u003c/article\u003e","loaded":true,"timedOut":false,"errorMessage":null,"headerInfo":{"toc":[{"level":1,"text":"Game-Ready Animation Library by Ready Player Me","anchor":"game-ready-animation-library-by-ready-player-me","htmlText":"Game-Ready Animation Library by Ready Player Me"},{"level":3,"text":"Version 1.0.0 - Published June 2023","anchor":"version-100---published-june-2023","htmlText":"Version 1.0.0 - Published June 2023"},{"level":3,"text":"Contents","anchor":"contents","htmlText":"Contents"},{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","htmlText":"Overview"},{"level":2,"text":"Animations","anchor":"animations","htmlText":"Animations"},{"level":3,"text":"Feminine Armature Animations","anchor":"feminine-armature-animations","htmlText":"Feminine Armature Animations"},{"level":3,"text":"Masculine Armature Animations","anchor":"masculine-armature-animations","htmlText":"Masculine Armature Animations"},{"level":2,"text":"FAQ","anchor":"faq","htmlText":"FAQ"},{"level":3,"text":"Are these animations really free?","anchor":"are-these-animations-really-free","htmlText":"Are these animations really free?"},{"level":3,"text":"Can I use these animations with characters that are not from Ready Player Me?","anchor":"can-i-use-these-animations-with-characters-that-are-not-from-ready-player-me","htmlText":"Can I use these animations with characters that are not from Ready Player Me?"},{"level":3,"text":"When will more animations be released?","anchor":"when-will-more-animations-be-released","htmlText":"When will more animations be released?"},{"level":3,"text":"What software do I need to use with these animations?","anchor":"what-software-do-i-need-to-use-with-these-animations","htmlText":"What software do I need to use with these animations?"},{"level":3,"text":"Where can I get help using these animations?","anchor":"where-can-i-get-help-using-these-animations","htmlText":"Where can I get help using these animations?"},{"level":2,"text":"Tutorials","anchor":"tutorials","htmlText":"Tutorials"},{"level":2,"text":"Notes","anchor":"notes","htmlText":"Notes"}],"siteNavLoginPath":"/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Freadyplayerme%2Fanimation-library"}},{"displayName":"LICENSE.md","repoName":"animation-library","refName":"master","path":"LICENSE.md","preferredFileType":"license","tabName":"License","richText":null,"loaded":false,"timedOut":false,"errorMessage":null,"headerInfo":{"toc":null,"siteNavLoginPath":"/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fg